mustard barbecue.

519
00:17:00,280 --> 00:17:01,880
Good, old Carolina
mustard barbecue.

520
00:17:01,880 --> 00:17:02,913
I'm a big fan.

521
00:17:02,913 --> 00:17:04,080
Prepared mustard.

522
00:17:04,080 --> 00:17:06,813
Salt, pepper, brown sugar,
chili powder...

523
00:17:06,813 --> 00:17:07,913
Tomato paste?
