553
00:18:04,186 --> 00:18:06,486
MAN:
And when you put a little bit of
the mustard sauce on top of it,

554
00:18:06,486 --> 00:18:07,953
oh, it's to die for.

555
00:18:07,953 --> 00:18:09,386
Can I get an order
of the brisket chili, please?

556
00:18:09,386 --> 00:18:10,920
You got it, man.

557
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:13,920
I've literally driven
over 50 miles to find them.

558
00:18:13,920 --> 00:18:16,586
FIERI: Which is either
setting up shop all over Spokane

559
00:18:16,586 --> 00:18:19,653
or working right here
in their hometown of Spangle.

560
00:18:19,653 --> 00:18:21,886
Was Spangle
ever a bigger town?

561
00:18:21,886 --> 00:18:25,320
No.
It was smaller, but...

562
00:18:25,320 --> 00:18:27,753
WOMAN: Community pride
for Nordic Smoke is amazing.

563
00:18:27,753 --> 00:18:28,953
We're pretty proud of them.

564
00:18:28,953 --> 00:18:31,086
Kacy's a veteran,
and the community really likes

565
00:18:31,086 --> 00:18:32,353
