569
00:18:35,586 --> 00:18:36,620
‐Yeah, appreciate that.
‐Really appreciate it.

570
00:18:36,620 --> 00:18:37,620
MAN: Well, the two brothers,
they take

571
00:18:37,620 --> 00:18:38,620
a lot of pride
in what they do.

572
00:18:38,620 --> 00:18:40,153
They go above and beyond
the call of duty

573
00:18:40,153 --> 00:18:41,653
