574
00:18:41,653 --> 00:18:44,086
Can I get ribs
and smoked beans, please?
SERVER: All right.

575
00:18:44,086 --> 00:18:45,686
The best ribs
I have ever had.

576
00:18:45,686 --> 00:18:47,686
MAN: The baked beans
are fantastic, too.

577
00:18:47,686 --> 00:18:49,353
It's a homemade family recipe

578
00:18:49,353 --> 00:18:51,153
that they've carried on
for generations.

579
00:18:51,153 --> 00:18:53,253
Okay, my brother,
St. Louis rib ‐‐

580
00:18:53,253 --> 00:18:55,520
