So, the same dry rub
that we did.

583
00:18:58,353 --> 00:19:00,093
Ready for the smoke, man.

584
00:19:00,093 --> 00:19:02,226
About five hours, 225.

585
00:19:02,226 --> 00:19:03,660
And just a little
apple cider spritz.

586
00:19:03,660 --> 00:19:04,760
Yep.
I hit it with that

587
00:19:04,760 --> 00:19:06,093
about every hour,

588
00:19:06,093 --> 00:19:08,226
and then there's
a honey‐maple beer glaze.

589
00:19:08,226 --> 00:19:09,293
Yeah.

590
00:19:09,293 --> 00:19:10,693
Did you fall a lot
as a kid?

591
00:19:10,693 --> 00:19:12,560
Oh, yeah.

592
00:19:12,560 --> 00:19:13,593
Time for the beans.

593
00:19:13,593 --> 00:19:14,726
‐Yep.
‐Now, whose recipe is this?

594
00:19:14,726 --> 00:19:15,826
Grandma's.

595
00:19:15,826 --> 00:19:18,093
So canned
pork and beans.
Yep.

596
00:19:18,093 --> 00:19:21,693
Black beans, red kidneys,
butter beans, onion,

597
00:19:21,693 --> 00:19:24,093
raw jalapeños,
brown sugar...
Okay.

598
00:19:24,093 --> 00:19:26,160
...ketchup,
apple cider vinegar.

599
00:19:26,160 --> 00:19:27,660
‐Fried‐up ground beef.
‐Yep.

600
00:19:27,660 --> 00:19:30,126
And then some
hickory‐smoked bacon crumbles.

601
00:19:30,126 --> 00:19:32,026
‐With the fat?
‐With the fat.

602
00:19:32,026 --> 00:19:34,326
What did she call this,
"Kitchen Sink"?
Yeah.

603
00:19:34,326 --> 00:19:36,060
And just some salt
and pepper, man.

604
00:19:36,060 --> 00:19:37,893
So, you're gonna bring
all that smoke flavor in.

605
00:19:37,893 --> 00:19:40,060
Yep.
225, about 4 hours.

606
00:19:40,060 --> 00:19:42,893
Okay.
Let's make it happen, Captain.

607
00:19:42,893 --> 00:19:44,560
All right, man.

608
00:19:44,560 --> 00:19:46,326
How many ribs you give
in an order?
Three.

609
00:19:46,326 --> 00:19:47,726
I don't need
any more than that.

610
00:19:47,726 --> 00:19:49,693
That's a big rib.

611
00:19:51,093 --> 00:19:53,060
Mmm.
Great smoke.

612
00:19:53,060 --> 00:19:54,226
You get the dry rub

613
00:19:54,226 --> 00:19:55,926
and then the mop
that you're throwing on there,

614
00:19:55,926 --> 00:19:59,600
