620
00:20:09,900 --> 00:20:12,800
Different textures
of the beans ‐‐

621
00:20:12,800 --> 00:20:14,300
the crunchy ground beef,

622
00:20:14,300 --> 00:20:18,666
the little nuggets of bacon
