you're giving away the recipe?

627
00:20:24,433 --> 00:20:25,833
Uh, no.

628
00:20:25,833 --> 00:20:27,866
We'll keep it
between us.
Okay.

629
00:20:27,866 --> 00:20:30,166
You guys,
don't tell anybody, okay?

630
00:20:30,166 --> 00:20:31,466
Ribs and beans.

631
00:20:31,466 --> 00:20:33,900
The ribs are my favorite
